title: Oscillons From The Anti-Sun
description:
Stereolab
Oscillons from the Anti-Sun [BOX SET]
Stereolab is one of my favourite bands, and this is a comprehensive box set-- a total beast of a package, spanning three full discs of EP material, over a time period stretching from 1993&#039;s Transient Random-Noise Bursts with Announcements to 2001&#039;s Sound-Dust.

Disc 1
1. Fluorescences
2. Allures
3. Fruition
4. Wow And Flutter
5. With Friends Like These
6. Pinball
7. Spinal Column
8. Ping Pong (Unreleased LP version)
9. Golden Ball
10. Cybele&#039;s Reverie
11. Nihilist Assault Group (parts 1, 2, 3)
12. Off-On

Disc 2	
1. Jenny Ondioline
2. Young Lungs
3. Escape Pod (From The World Of Medical Observations)
4. Moodles
5. You Used To Call Me Sadness
6. Captain Easychord
7. Les Aimies Des Memes
8. French Disco
9. Transona Five (Live)
10. Moogie Wonderland
11. Canned Candies
12. Narco Martenot

Disc 3
1. The Noise Of Carpet
2. The Free Design
3. Les Yper-Yper Sound
4. Pain Et Spectacles
5. Ping Pong (Single Version)
6. Long Life Love
7. Jenny Ondionline (Alternate Version)
8. Heavy Denim
9. Brigitte
10. Miss Modular
11. Soop Groove #1
